  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.4.7">
<l>poṅkilaṅku purinūlun tōlun tāḻap pollāta kuṟaḷuruvāyp poruntā vāṇaṉ</l>
<l>maṅkalamcēr maṟaivēḷvi yataṉuḷ pukku maṇṇakalaṅ kuṟaiyiranta maintaṉ kaṇṭīr</l>
<l>koṅkalarnta malarkkuḻalār koṅkai tōynta kuṅkumattiṉ kuḻampaḷainta kōlan taṉṉāl</l>
<l>ceṅkalaṅkal veṇmaṇalmēl tavaḻum nāṅkūrt tiruteṟṟi yampalatteṉ ceṅkaṇ mālē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The man who, in the form of an incomparable dwarf</l>
<l rend="indent">as an attractive, bright twisted thread and a [deer]skin hung [on his body],</l>
<l>Entering the auspicious Vedic sacrifice of the dislikable, prosperous man,</l>
<l rend="indent">begged for want of a span of earth, you see,</l>
<l>Is my bright-eyed Māl in Tirutteṟṟiyampalam in Nāṅkūr,</l>
<l rend="indent">where red rivulets trickle on white sand</l>
<l>From the designs of mixed kumkuma paste smeared on the breasts</l>
<l rend="indent">of those with flowered curls where fragrance wafts.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
